  1ŌåÆ// ŌöĆŌöĆ SessionList Preact component ŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆ
  2ŌåÆ//
  3ŌåÆ// Replaces the imperative renderSessionList() with a reactive Preact
  4ŌåÆ// component that auto-rerenders from sessionStore signals.
  5ŌåÆ
  6ŌåÆimport { html } from "htm/preact";
  7ŌåÆimport { useEffect, useRef } from "preact/hooks";
  8ŌåÆimport {
  9ŌåÆ	makeBranchIcon,
 10ŌåÆ	makeChatIcon,
 11ŌåÆ	makeCronIcon,
 12ŌåÆ	makeDiscordIcon,
 13ŌåÆ	makeProjectIcon,
 14ŌåÆ	makeTeamsIcon,
 15ŌåÆ	makeTelegramIcon,
 16ŌåÆ} from "../icons.js";
 17ŌåÆimport { currentPrefix, navigate, sessionPath } from "../router.js";
 18ŌåÆimport { switchSession } from "../sessions.js";
 19ŌåÆimport { projectStore } from "../stores/project-store.js";
 20ŌåÆimport { sessionStore } from "../stores/session-store.js";
 21ŌåÆ
 22ŌåÆ// ŌöĆŌöĆ Braille spinner ŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆ
 23ŌåÆvar spinnerFrames = [
 24ŌåÆ	"\u280B",
 25ŌåÆ	"\u2819",
 26ŌåÆ	"\u2839",
 27ŌåÆ	"\u2838",
 28ŌåÆ	"\u283C",
 29ŌåÆ	"\u2834",
 30ŌåÆ	"\u2826",
 31ŌåÆ	"\u2827",
 32ŌåÆ	"\u2807",
 33ŌåÆ	"\u280F",
 34ŌåÆ];
 35ŌåÆ
 36ŌåÆ// ŌöĆŌöĆ Helpers ŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆ
 37ŌåÆ
 38ŌåÆfunction channelSessionType(s) {
 39ŌåÆ	var key = s.key || "";
 40ŌåÆ	if (key.startsWith("telegram:")) return "telegram";
 41ŌåÆ	if (key.startsWith("msteams:")) return "msteams";
 42ŌåÆ	if (key.startsWith("discord:")) return "discord";
 43ŌåÆ	var binding = s.channelBinding || null;
 44ŌåÆ	if (!binding) return null;
 45ŌåÆ	try {
 46ŌåÆ		return JSON.parse(binding).channel_type || null;
 47ŌåÆ	} catch (_e) {
 48ŌåÆ		return null;
 49ŌåÆ	}
 50ŌåÆ}
 51ŌåÆ
 52ŌåÆfunction formatHHMM(epochMs) {
 53ŌåÆ	return new Date(epochMs).toLocaleTimeString(undefined, { hour: "2-digit", minute: "2-digit" });
 54ŌåÆ}
 55ŌåÆ
 56ŌåÆ// ŌöĆŌöĆ Icon component (renders SVG icon into a ref) ŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆ
 57ŌåÆfunction SessionIcon({ session, isBranch }) {
 58ŌåÆ	var iconRef = useRef(null);
 59ŌåÆ	useEffect(() => {
 60ŌåÆ		if (!iconRef.current) return;
 61ŌåÆ		iconRef.current.textContent = "";
 62ŌåÆ		var key = session.key || "";
 63ŌåÆ		var icon;
 64ŌåÆ		var channelType = channelSessionType(session);
 65ŌåÆ		if (isBranch) icon = makeBranchIcon();
 66ŌåÆ		else if (key.startsWith("cron:")) icon = makeCronIcon();
 67ŌåÆ		else if (channelType === "telegram") icon = makeTelegramIcon();
 68ŌåÆ		else if (channelType === "msteams") icon = makeTeamsIcon();
 69ŌåÆ		else if (channelType === "discord") icon = makeDiscordIcon();
 70ŌåÆ		else icon = makeChatIcon();
 71ŌåÆ		iconRef.current.appendChild(icon);
 72ŌåÆ	}, [session.key, isBranch]);
 73ŌåÆ
 74ŌåÆ	var channelType = channelSessionType(session);
 75ŌåÆ	var channelBound = Boolean(channelType);
 76ŌåÆ	var iconStyle = {};
 77ŌåÆ	if (channelBound) {
 78ŌåÆ		iconStyle.color = session.activeChannel ? "var(--accent)" : "var(--muted)";
 79ŌåÆ		iconStyle.opacity = session.activeChannel ? "1" : "0.5";
 80ŌåÆ	} else {
 81ŌåÆ		iconStyle.color = "var(--muted)";
 82ŌåÆ	}
 83ŌåÆ	var channelLabel = channelType === "msteams" ? "Microsoft Teams" : channelType === "discord" ? "Discord" : "Telegram";
 84ŌåÆ	var title = channelBound
 85ŌåÆ		? session.activeChannel
 86ŌåÆ			? `Active ${channelLabel} session`
 87ŌåÆ			: `${channelLabel} session (inactive)`
 88ŌåÆ		: "";
 89ŌåÆ
 90ŌåÆ	// Read the reactive signal ŌĆö auto-subscribes for badge updates.
 91ŌåÆ	var count = session.badgeCount.value;
 92ŌåÆ
 93ŌåÆ	return html`
 94ŌåÆ		<span class="session-icon" style=${iconStyle} title=${title}>
 95ŌåÆ			<span ref=${iconRef}></span>
 96ŌåÆ			<span class="session-spinner"></span>
 97ŌåÆ			${
 98ŌåÆ				count > 0 &&
 99ŌåÆ				html`
100ŌåÆ				<span class="session-badge" data-session-key=${session.key}>
101ŌåÆ					${count > 99 ? "99+" : String(count)}
102ŌåÆ				</span>
103ŌåÆ			`
104ŌåÆ			}
105ŌåÆ		</span>
106ŌåÆ	`;
107ŌåÆ}
108ŌåÆ
109ŌåÆ// ŌöĆŌöĆ Session meta (fork, worktree, project) ŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆ
110ŌåÆfunction SessionMeta({ session }) {
111ŌåÆ	var ref = useRef(null);
112ŌåÆ
113ŌåÆ	useEffect(() => {
114ŌåÆ		if (!ref.current) return;
115ŌåÆ		ref.current.textContent = "";
116ŌåÆ
117ŌåÆ		var parts = [];
118ŌåÆ		if (session.forkPoint != null) parts.push(`fork@${session.forkPoint}`);
119ŌåÆ		var branch = session.worktree_branch || "";
120ŌåÆ		if (branch) parts.push(`\u2387 ${branch}`);
121ŌåÆ
122ŌåÆ		var projId = session.projectId || "";
123ŌåÆ		var proj = projId ? projectStore.getById(projId) : null;
124ŌåÆ
125ŌåÆ		if (parts.length === 0 && !proj) return;
126ŌåÆ
127ŌåÆ		ref.current.textContent = parts.join(" \u00b7 ");
128ŌåÆ		if (proj) {
129ŌåÆ			if (parts.length > 0) ref.current.appendChild(document.createTextNode(" \u00b7 "));
130ŌåÆ			var icon = makeProjectIcon();
131ŌåÆ			icon.style.display = "inline";
132ŌåÆ			icon.style.verticalAlign = "-1px";
133ŌåÆ			icon.style.marginRight = "2px";
134ŌåÆ			icon.style.opacity = "0.7";
135ŌåÆ			ref.current.appendChild(icon);
136ŌåÆ			ref.current.appendChild(document.createTextNode(proj.label || proj.id));
137ŌåÆ		}
138ŌåÆ	}, [session.projectId, session.forkPoint, session.worktree_branch]);
139ŌåÆ
140ŌåÆ	return html`<div class="session-meta" data-session-key=${session.key} ref=${ref}></div>`;
141ŌåÆ}
142ŌåÆ
143ŌåÆ// ŌöĆŌöĆ SessionItem component ŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆ
144ŌåÆfunction SessionItem({ session, activeKey, depth, keyMap, refreshing }) {
145ŌåÆ	var isBranch = depth > 0;
146ŌåÆ	var active = session.key === activeKey;
147ŌåÆ	// Read per-session signals ŌĆö auto-subscribes for re-render.
148ŌåÆ	// dataVersion triggers re-render when plain properties (preview,
149ŌåÆ	// updatedAt, label) change. Badge updates come from badgeCount
150ŌåÆ	// signal read inside SessionIcon.
151ŌåÆ	var replying = session.replying.value;
152ŌåÆ	session.dataVersion.value;
153ŌåÆ	// Unread tint: true when not viewing this session and there are messages
154ŌåÆ	// beyond what we last saw (badgeCount is reactive, triggers re-render).
155ŌåÆ	var badge = session.badgeCount.value;
156ŌåÆ	var unread = session.localUnread.value || (!active && badge > (session.lastSeenMessageCount || 0));
157ŌåÆ
158ŌåÆ	var className = "session-item";
159ŌåÆ	if (active) className += " active";
160ŌåÆ	if (unread) className += " unread";
161ŌåÆ	if (replying) className += " replying";
162ŌåÆ	if (refreshing) className += " loading";
163ŌåÆ
164ŌåÆ	var style = isBranch ? { paddingLeft: `${12 + depth * 16}px` } : {};
165ŌåÆ
166ŌåÆ	var rawPreview = session.preview || "";
167ŌåÆ	var parentPreview =
168ŌåÆ		session.parentSessionKey && keyMap[session.parentSessionKey] ? keyMap[session.parentSessionKey].preview || "" : "";
169ŌåÆ	var preview = rawPreview && rawPreview === parentPreview ? "" : rawPreview;
170ŌåÆ	var ts = session.updatedAt || 0;
171ŌåÆ	var agentId = session.agent_id || "main";
172ŌåÆ	var showAgentBadge = !!agentId && agentId !== "main";
173ŌåÆ
174ŌåÆ	function onClick() {
175ŌåÆ		if (currentPrefix !== "/chats") {
176ŌåÆ			navigate(sessionPath(session.key));
177ŌåÆ		} else {
178ŌåÆ			switchSession(session.key);
179ŌåÆ		}
180ŌåÆ	}
181ŌåÆ
182ŌåÆ	return html`
183ŌåÆ		<div class=${className} data-session-key=${session.key} style=${style} onClick=${onClick}>
184ŌåÆ			<div class="session-info">
185ŌåÆ				<div class="session-label">
186ŌåÆ					<${SessionIcon} session=${session} isBranch=${isBranch} />
187ŌåÆ					<span data-label-text>${session.label || session.key}</span>
188ŌåÆ					${
189ŌåÆ						showAgentBadge &&
190ŌåÆ						html`
191ŌåÆ						<span
192ŌåÆ							class="text-[10px] text-[var(--muted)] border border-[var(--border)] rounded px-1 py-0 ml-1"
193ŌåÆ							title=${`Agent: ${agentId}`}
194ŌåÆ						>
195ŌåÆ							@${agentId}
196ŌåÆ						</span>
197ŌåÆ					`
198ŌåÆ					}
199ŌåÆ					${
200ŌåÆ						ts > 0 &&
201ŌåÆ						html`
202ŌåÆ						<span class="session-time" title=${new Date(ts).toLocaleString()}>
203ŌåÆ							${formatHHMM(ts)}
204ŌåÆ						</span>
205ŌåÆ					`
206ŌåÆ					}
207ŌåÆ				</div>
208ŌåÆ				${preview && html`<div class="session-preview">${preview}</div>`}
209ŌåÆ				<${SessionMeta} session=${session} />
210ŌåÆ			</div>
211ŌåÆ		</div>
212ŌåÆ	`;
213ŌåÆ}
214ŌåÆ
215ŌåÆ// ŌöĆŌöĆ SessionList component ŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆ
216ŌåÆexport function SessionList() {
217ŌåÆ	var allSessions = sessionStore.sessions.value;
218ŌåÆ	var activeKey = sessionStore.activeSessionKey.value;
219ŌåÆ	var refreshingKey = sessionStore.refreshInProgressKey.value;
220ŌåÆ	var filterId = projectStore.projectFilterId.value;
221ŌåÆ	var tab = sessionStore.sessionListTab.value;
222ŌåÆ
223ŌåÆ	// Spinner animation via setInterval
224ŌåÆ	var spinnersRef = useRef(null);
225ŌåÆ	useEffect(() => {
226ŌåÆ		var idx = 0;
227ŌåÆ		var timer = setInterval(() => {
228ŌåÆ			idx = (idx + 1) % spinnerFrames.length;
229ŌåÆ			if (!spinnersRef.current) return;
230ŌåÆ			var els = spinnersRef.current.querySelectorAll(
231ŌåÆ				".session-item.replying .session-spinner, .session-item.loading .session-spinner",
232ŌåÆ			);
233ŌåÆ			for (var el of els) el.textContent = spinnerFrames[idx];
234ŌåÆ		}, 80);
235ŌåÆ		return () => clearInterval(timer);
236ŌåÆ	}, []);
237ŌåÆ
238ŌåÆ	var filtered = filterId ? allSessions.filter((s) => s.projectId === filterId) : allSessions;
239ŌåÆ	if (tab === "sessions") {
240ŌåÆ		filtered = filtered.filter((s) => !(s.key || "").startsWith("cron:"));
241ŌåÆ	} else if (tab === "cron") {
242ŌåÆ		filtered = filtered.filter((s) => (s.key || "").startsWith("cron:"));
243ŌåÆ	}
244ŌåÆ
245ŌåÆ	// Build parentŌåÆchildren map for tree rendering
246ŌåÆ	var childrenMap = {};
247ŌåÆ	var keyMap = {};
248ŌåÆ	filtered.forEach((s) => {
249ŌåÆ		keyMap[s.key] = s;
250ŌåÆ		if (s.parentSessionKey) {
251ŌåÆ			if (!childrenMap[s.parentSessionKey]) childrenMap[s.parentSessionKey] = [];
252ŌåÆ			childrenMap[s.parentSessionKey].push(s);
253ŌåÆ		}
254ŌåÆ	});
255ŌåÆ	var roots = filtered.filter((s) => !(s.parentSessionKey && keyMap[s.parentSessionKey]));
256ŌåÆ
257ŌåÆ	function renderTree(session, depth) {
258ŌåÆ		var children = childrenMap[session.key] || [];
259ŌåÆ		return html`
260ŌåÆ			<${SessionItem}
261ŌåÆ				key=${session.key}
262ŌåÆ				session=${session}
263ŌåÆ				activeKey=${activeKey}
264ŌåÆ				depth=${depth}
265ŌåÆ				keyMap=${keyMap}
266ŌåÆ				refreshing=${session.key === refreshingKey}
267ŌåÆ			/>
268ŌåÆ			${children.map((child) => renderTree(child, depth + 1))}
269ŌåÆ		`;
270ŌåÆ	}
271ŌåÆ
272ŌåÆ	return html`
273ŌåÆ		<div ref=${spinnersRef}>
274ŌåÆ			${roots.map((s) => renderTree(s, 0))}
275ŌåÆ		</div>
276ŌåÆ	`;
277ŌåÆ}
278ŌåÆ

  1ŌåÆ// ŌöĆŌöĆ SessionHeader Preact component ŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆ
  2ŌåÆ//
  3ŌåÆ// Replaces the imperative updateChatSessionHeader() with a reactive
  4ŌåÆ// Preact component reading sessionStore.activeSession.
  5ŌåÆ
  6ŌåÆimport { html } from "htm/preact";
  7ŌåÆimport { useCallback, useEffect, useRef, useState } from "preact/hooks";
  8ŌåÆimport { onEvent } from "../events.js";
  9ŌåÆimport * as gon from "../gon.js";
 10ŌåÆimport { parseAgentsListPayload, sendRpc } from "../helpers.js";
 11ŌåÆimport {
 12ŌåÆ	clearActiveSession,
 13ŌåÆ	fetchSessions,
 14ŌåÆ	setSessionActiveRunId,
 15ŌåÆ	setSessionReplying,
 16ŌåÆ	switchSession,
 17ŌåÆ} from "../sessions.js";
 18ŌåÆimport { sessionStore } from "../stores/session-store.js";
 19ŌåÆimport { ComboSelect, confirmDialog, shareLinkDialog, shareVisibilityDialog, showToast } from "../ui.js";
 20ŌåÆ
 21ŌåÆfunction nextSessionKey(currentKey) {
 22ŌåÆ	var allSessions = sessionStore.sessions.value;
 23ŌåÆ	var s = allSessions.find((x) => x.key === currentKey);
 24ŌåÆ	if (s?.parentSessionKey) return s.parentSessionKey;
 25ŌåÆ	var idx = allSessions.findIndex((x) => x.key === currentKey);
 26ŌåÆ	if (idx >= 0 && idx + 1 < allSessions.length) return allSessions[idx + 1].key;
 27ŌåÆ	if (idx > 0) return allSessions[idx - 1].key;
 28ŌåÆ	return "main";
 29ŌåÆ}
 30ŌåÆ
 31ŌåÆfunction buildShareUrl(payload) {
 32ŌåÆ	var url = `${window.location.origin}${payload.path}`;
 33ŌåÆ	if (payload.accessKey) {
 34ŌåÆ		url += `?k=${encodeURIComponent(payload.accessKey)}`;
 35ŌåÆ	}
 36ŌåÆ	return url;
 37ŌåÆ}
 38ŌåÆ
 39ŌåÆfunction isSshTargetNode(node) {
 40ŌåÆ	return node?.platform === "ssh" || String(node?.nodeId || "").startsWith("ssh:");
 41ŌåÆ}
 42ŌåÆ
 43ŌåÆfunction nodeOptionLabel(node) {
 44ŌåÆ	if (!node) return "Local";
 45ŌåÆ	if (node.displayName) return node.displayName;
 46ŌåÆ	if (isSshTargetNode(node)) {
 47ŌåÆ		var target = String(node.nodeId || "").replace(/^ssh:/, "");
 48ŌåÆ		return `SSH: ${target}`;
 49ŌåÆ	}
 50ŌåÆ	return node.nodeId;
 51ŌåÆ}
 52ŌåÆ
 53ŌåÆasync function copyShareUrl(url, visibility) {
 54ŌåÆ	try {
 55ŌåÆ		if (navigator.clipboard?.writeText) {
 56ŌåÆ			await navigator.clipboard.writeText(url);
 57ŌåÆ			showToast("Share link copied", "success");
 58ŌåÆ			return;
 59ŌåÆ		}
 60ŌåÆ	} catch (_err) {
 61ŌåÆ		// Clipboard APIs can fail on some browsers/permissions.
 62ŌåÆ	}
 63ŌåÆ	await shareLinkDialog(url, visibility);
 64ŌåÆ}
 65ŌåÆ
 66ŌåÆexport function SessionHeader({
 67ŌåÆ	showSelectors = true,
 68ŌåÆ	showName = true,
 69ŌåÆ	showShare = true,
 70ŌåÆ	showFork = true,
 71ŌåÆ	showStop = true,
 72ŌåÆ	showClear = true,
 73ŌåÆ	showDelete = true,
 74ŌåÆ	nameOwnLine = false,
 75ŌåÆ	showRenameButton = false,
 76ŌåÆ	actionButtonClass = "chat-session-btn",
 77ŌåÆ	onBeforeShare = null,
 78ŌåÆ	onBeforeDelete = null,
 79ŌåÆ} = {}) {
 80ŌåÆ	var session = sessionStore.activeSession.value;
 81ŌåÆ	var currentKey = sessionStore.activeSessionKey.value;
 82ŌåÆ	var gonAgentsPayload = parseAgentsListPayload(gon.get("agents"));
 83ŌåÆ	var initialAgentOptions = Array.isArray(gonAgentsPayload?.agents) ? gonAgentsPayload.agents : [];
 84ŌåÆ	var initialDefaultAgentId = typeof gonAgentsPayload?.defaultId === "string" ? gonAgentsPayload.defaultId : "main";
 85ŌåÆ
 86ŌåÆ	var [renaming, setRenaming] = useState(false);
 87ŌåÆ	var [clearing, setClearing] = useState(false);
 88ŌåÆ	var [stopping, setStopping] = useState(false);
 89ŌåÆ	var [switchingAgent, setSwitchingAgent] = useState(false);
 90ŌåÆ	var [agentOptions, setAgentOptions] = useState(initialAgentOptions);
 91ŌåÆ	var [defaultAgentId, setDefaultAgentId] = useState(initialDefaultAgentId);
 92ŌåÆ	var [agentOptionsLoaded, setAgentOptionsLoaded] = useState(initialAgentOptions.length > 0);
 93ŌåÆ	var [nodeOptions, setNodeOptions] = useState([]);
 94ŌåÆ	var [switchingNode, setSwitchingNode] = useState(false);
 95ŌåÆ	var inputRef = useRef(null);
 96ŌåÆ
 97ŌåÆ	var fullName = session ? session.label || session.key : currentKey;
 98ŌåÆ	var displayName = nameOwnLine ? fullName : fullName.length > 20 ? `${fullName.slice(0, 20)}\u2026` : fullName;
 99ŌåÆ	var replying = session?.replying.value;
100ŌåÆ	var activeRunId = session?.activeRunId.value || null;
101ŌåÆ
102ŌåÆ	var isMain = currentKey === "main";
